msgctxt "body.59de109a-d749-4c00-84b2-f10cf36546ba.title"
msgid "What we’ll build together"
msgstr "Què construirem junts"

msgctxt "body.ac3d9b8b-d7c0-45ad-ac74-bbb1f209e415.left_column.5b701ac4-2e77-4132-9a11-07fff71a8c38"
msgid "The Stack in the Wild"
msgstr "The Stack in the Wild"

msgctxt "body.ac3d9b8b-d7c0-45ad-ac74-bbb1f209e415.left_column.f3cf20be-f8af-4a3b-b484-d9f8b3407119"
msgid "Opinionated, deployable open source AI stacks. Closing the gap between \"here's a model\" and \"here's a system you can actually run in production.\""
msgstr "Piles d'IA de codi obert amb criteri propi i desplegables. Tancarem la bretxa entre «vet aquí un model» i «vet aquí un sistema que realment podeu executar en la vostra producció»."

msgctxt "body.ac3d9b8b-d7c0-45ad-ac74-bbb1f209e415.right_column.2d9a4060-27da-4f16-bb0a-57fe322db4ee"
msgid "Agents in the Wild"
msgstr "Agents in the Wild"

msgctxt "body.ac3d9b8b-d7c0-45ad-ac74-bbb1f209e415.right_column.5fd88e67-b95c-4087-98d0-60f7e64316bf"
msgid "The real security posture of agentic AI. Capability models, adversarial testing, and what \"secure enough to deploy\" means when agents are already shipping."
msgstr "La postura de seguretat real de la IA agentiva. Models de capacitat, proves d'adversari i què significa «prou segur per desplegar-lo» quan els agents ja estan funcionant."

msgctxt "body.45795a8d-d53c-46cb-a629-8a283c0a6cd3.left_column.fcdb4212-bfb7-4349-b012-5c9182c1e9e0"
msgid "Running Wild on Local Hardware"
msgstr "Running Wild on Local Hardware"

msgctxt "body.45795a8d-d53c-46cb-a629-8a283c0a6cd3.left_column.0dfe0299-89f7-409f-b555-550b5224098b"
msgid "AI on devices people already own. Local inference, custom silicon, and the shrinking gap between data center and laptop."
msgstr "IA en dispositius que la gent ja té. Inferència local, silici personalitzat i una bretxa més petita entre el centre de dades i el portàtil."

msgctxt "body.45795a8d-d53c-46cb-a629-8a283c0a6cd3.right_column.ac9c46ae-6181-4c07-b9cf-ff74dea3553b"
msgid "Standards Before the Garden Walls"
msgstr "Standards Before the Garden Walls"

msgctxt "body.45795a8d-d53c-46cb-a629-8a283c0a6cd3.right_column.62229bd4-0ce1-4a9d-b0a3-04eb77c09c72"
msgid "Agent protocols, identity, payments, memory portability. The standards being written right now that will shape the next decade."
msgstr "Protocols d'agents, identitat, pagaments, portabilitat de la memòria. Els estàndards que s'estan definint ara mateix i que conformaran la propera dècada."

msgctxt "body.5376a5ae-8fa4-4851-8dde-b636010ec2d5.heading"
msgid "If this is you, join us"
msgstr "Si tot això us ressona, no falteu"

msgctxt "body.5376a5ae-8fa4-4851-8dde-b636010ec2d5.items.bf29c01f-e130-460b-aed3-b4605375a2cf.title"
msgid "Founders &amp; CTOs"
msgstr "Fundadors i CTO"

msgctxt "body.5376a5ae-8fa4-4851-8dde-b636010ec2d5.items.bf29c01f-e130-460b-aed3-b4605375a2cf.description"
msgid "Betting your company on an open stack. Talk about the bet and what it cost to make it real."
msgstr "Apostar a la vostra empresa per l'open stack. Parleu-ne i valoreu quant costa fer-ho realitat."

msgctxt "body.5376a5ae-8fa4-4851-8dde-b636010ec2d5.items.93d22d6c-2af7-48b3-b787-27c162452793.title"
msgid "Principal Engineers and Staff Architects"
msgstr "Enginyers principals i arquitectes en plantilla"

msgctxt "body.5376a5ae-8fa4-4851-8dde-b636010ec2d5.items.93d22d6c-2af7-48b3-b787-27c162452793.description"
msgid "Running open source AI in production. The pipeline, the failure modes, the call you regret making."
msgstr "Executar IA de codi obert en la producció. El pipeline, els modes d'avaria, la decisió que lamentes haver pres."

msgctxt "body.5376a5ae-8fa4-4851-8dde-b636010ec2d5.items.442865eb-0292-4494-b12e-32093b33bdea.title"
msgid "Security &amp; Safety Leads"
msgstr "Responsables de seguretat i protecció"

msgctxt "body.5376a5ae-8fa4-4851-8dde-b636010ec2d5.items.442865eb-0292-4494-b12e-32093b33bdea.description"
msgid "Owning the threat model for agentic systems already shipping. What \"secure enough\" actually looks like."
msgstr "Gestionar el model d'amenaces per a sistemes agentius que ja estan funcionant. Què vol dir que siguin \"prou segurs\"."

msgctxt "body.5376a5ae-8fa4-4851-8dde-b636010ec2d5.items.6b642234-ac37-424c-8310-f76104e581a5.title"
msgid "Standards Participants"
msgstr "Participants"

msgctxt "body.5376a5ae-8fa4-4851-8dde-b636010ec2d5.items.6b642234-ac37-424c-8310-f76104e581a5.description"
msgid "Shaping the agentic web before the walls go up. Protocols, identity, payments, memory."
msgstr "Donar forma al web agentiu abans que s'acabi de construir. Protocols, identitat, pagaments, memòria."

msgctxt "body.b1042f30-74a7-49e4-9ae1-9523abe8b577.left_column.6a6c2d35-9b93-4c67-ae0f-e5435640ceec"
